# Implementation Plan - Fix HBV Printing Bug & Fix Nested Sub-item Extraction & Selection Bug

The goal is to fix a bug where text from unselected sub-items (like "Right" in Hemiparesis) is incorrectly included in the PDF summary, and to ensure that sub-items are correctly selected and identified. This will also improve the reliability of automated testing and provide a cleaner way to fix the reported HBV printing bug.

## Proposed Changes

### [HTML Structure Standardization]

Convert in-line sub-options to standard nested `<ul>` structures. This ensures the [getRecursivelyCheckedText](file:///c:/Users/A03772/.gemini/antigravity/Combined_Server/SurgerySchedule/templates/legacy_schedule.html#3905-3933) and [isLiChecked](file:///c:/Users/A03772/.gemini/antigravity/Combined_Server/SurgerySchedule/templates/legacy_schedule.html#3934-4015) functions work reliably.

Affected sections:
#### [MODIFY] [legacy_schedule.html](file:///c:/Users/A03772/.gemini/antigravity/Combined_Server/SurgerySchedule/templates/legacy_schedule.html)
- **Cardiovascular**: Atrial fibrillation, AV Block.
- **Neurologic**: Hemiparesis.
- **Respiratory**: Asthma Classification.
- **Anesthesia Plan**: Bronchoscope options.

